ParLocationGroup is a BusinessClass
    owned by ic
    prefix is PLGR

    Ontology
        symbolic key is ParLocationGroup

    Patterns
        implements StaticJava

    Persistent Fields
        Description
        Room                    is AlphaUpper size 20
        Active                  is Boolean

    Sets
        ByRoom 
            Sort Order
                Company
                Room
                ParLocationGroup

    Conditions
        RecordExist
			restricted
			when (ParLocationGroup exists)

	Relations

		ParLocationGroupRoomRel
			one-to-many relation to ParLocationGroup
			Field Mapping uses ByRoom
				related.Company	                = Company 
				related.Room                    = Room

	Field Rules
		Room
			constraint (ParLocationGroupRoomRel not exists)
				"ParLocationGroupForRoom<Room>AlreadyExists"

		Active
			initial value is true	

	Actions		
        Create is a Create Action
        Update is an Update Action
        Delete is a Delete Action
            
